## Exclude build artefacts — keeps the Docker build context small and fast.
## These directories are recreated by dotnet restore/build inside the container.

**/bin/
**/obj/

## IDE / OS artefacts
**/.vs/
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
**/*.user
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store

## Git
.git/
.gitignore
.gitattributes

## Docker files themselves (no need to copy into the image)
docker-compose.yml
docker-compose.override.yml
**/*.Dockerfile
**/Dockerfile

## RabbitMQ config (mounted as volumes by docker-compose, not baked into images)
rabbitmq/

## Markdown and docs
*.md
